0-03-06T04:13:25.000Z","msg":"射死支那賤畜<br />\n<br />\n想消滅支那，我們就要帶領支畜暴動和革命，才有機會從內部瓦解支共（輸出革命+加速主義，缺一不可）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1911527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1911527</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1e6f83a16ac2086407e09e3fa889c78d425933ac","tid":1912351,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T04:17:26.000Z","msg":"啲官方fb真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e240984402c5d495513fee9d19403e6d87371f79","tid":1912351,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T04:25:30.000Z","msg":"G持<br />\n射撚死班生蕃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a205ff75b1e3facb57a07fb9dc65344d027d4e2","tid":1912351,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e6f83a16ac2086407e09e3fa889c78d425933ac","tid":1912351,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T04:17:26.000Z","msg":"啲官方fb真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T08:10:00.000Z","msg":"蔡英文2018大敗之後 決定要貼地 所以用memes治國"}]}